) platinum credit cards .
he got cold and wet a few times , worried about finding gas , did n't always have hotel rooms up to his standards , and had delays at some borders , yawn .
the adventure must have been resisting the urge to buy an airline ticket back to new york using one of his many visa cards .
i rode a bicycle around the world for 19 months at about the same time mr. rogers was having his " adventure .
" i am stunned that he perceived so little in his long travels .
i do n't know how someone could travel in foreign countries that extensively and end up completely unchanged by the experience .
