he spends little time on the finer elements of sniper tradecraft , training and shooting .
this can be found elsewhere .
overall this book was a great disappointment .
if only a fraction of coughlin 's self-acclaimed exploits are true , then he is a remarkable sniper .
he should let his accomplishments speak for themselves and not try to beat us over the head with them

